hadiths[111]{hadithnumber,text}:
3087,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Makka Mukarrama sey nikaley gaey to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : un logon (mushrekine-Makka) ney apney Nabi ko nikal diya :  (اِنَّا لِلّٰہِ وَاِنَّا اِلَیْہِ رَاجِعُوْنَ),""ab ye log zarur tabah aur barbad hongey'' phir ye aayat utri :(اُذِنَ لِلَّذِیْنَ یُقٰتَلُوْنَ … … عَلیٰ نَصْرِھِمْ لَقَدِیْرٌ), ''jinn logon sey bila wajah ladaai ki jati hai, unhen bhi ladney (jihad) ki ijazat di jati hai kyonkey wo mazloom hain aur yaqinan Allah Taala un ki madad karney par zarur qadir hai. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke ab an-qareeb kafiron sey ladaai hogi. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke ladaai key (jawaz key) barey mein ye sab sey pehli aayat thi jo utri."
3088,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) aur unkey kuchh sathi Makka Mukarrama mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum kafir mushrik they to izzat waley they, jab hum musalman huye to zaleel ho gaey. aap ney farmaya : (filhaal) mujhey maaf aur darguzar karney ka hukm diya gaya hai, lihaza tum ladaai na lado. phir jab hum Allah Taala key hukm sey Madina Munawra pahunch gaey to Allah Taala ney hamein ladney ka hukm diya, lekin baaz musalman ladaai sey rukey rahey to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (اَلَمْ تَرَالِیَ الَّذِیْنَ قِیْلَ لَھُمْ کُفُّوْآ اَیْدِیَکُمْ وَاَقِیْمُوالصَّلٰوۃ),''(aey Nabi ! ) kya aap ney un logon ko nahin dekha jin sey kaha gaya tha ke tum apney haath (ladaai sey) rokey rakho aur namaz qaaim karo.''"
3089,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey Jaamey kalimaat dey kar bheja gaya hai aur mujhey roab dey kar meri madad ki gaee hai. eik dafa main soyaa huwa tha ke merey paas zamin key khazanon ki chabiyan laee gaeen aur merey haath par rakh di gaeen. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) to (duniya sey) chaley gaey, tum un khazanon ko nikal rahey ho."
3090,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko usi (sabiqa hadees ki) tarah farmatey suna.
3091,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : mujhey Jaamey kalimaat dey kar bheja gaya hai aur roab dey kar meri madad ki gaee hai. aur eik dafa main soyaa huwa tha ke merey paas zamin key khazanon ki chabiyan laee gaeen aur merey haath par rakh di gaeen. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) to (duniya sey) tashrif ley gaey lekin tum un khazanon ko nikal rahey ho.
3092,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladaai ladun yahan tak ke wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh lein. jis aadmi ney (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh liya, us ney mujh sey apni jaan aur maal ko mehfooz kar liya. siwaey iske ke uskey zimmey kisi ka haq adaa hone se baqi reh gaya ho.baaqi raha uska haqeeqi hisab to wo Allah Taala key zimmey hai."
3093,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut huye aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa banaaey gaey aur baaz Arab logon ney kufr kiya (aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey ladaai ka irada farmaya) to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Abu-Bakar ! aap un logon sey kaisey ladaai ladengey jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : mujhey logon sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh len? jo shakhs (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh ley, us ney mujh sey apni jaan aur maal ko bacha liya siwaey iske ke is par kisi ka haq banta ho. aur us ka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main un logon sey zarur ladunga jo namaz aur Zakat mein farq kartey hain kyonkey Zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey bakri ka bachcha deney sey inkar karen jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is baat par bhi un sey ladunga. (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) Allah ki qism ! mujhey saaf samajh mein aa gaya ke Allah Taala ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina ladaai key liye khol diya hai aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya hai ke yehi baat bar-haq hai."
3094,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya aur bahut sey Arab log kafir ban gaey to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Abu-Bakar ! aap un logon sey kaisey ladaai kerengey jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hai : mujhey logon sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ) padh len. jis shakhs ney (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh liya, us ney mujh sey apna jaan aur maal mehfooz kar liya, siwaey iske ke is par kisi ka haq banta ho. baqi raha us ka hisab to wo Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main un logon sey zarur ladunga jinhoney namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq kar di hai kyonkey Zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey bakri ka bachcha na den jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they tab bhi main un sey ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey malum ho gaya ke Allah Taala ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina ladaai key liye khol diya hai, to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke yehi baat bar-haq hai. (Imam Nasai ney kaha : hadees key ye mazkura) alfaz (ustaad) Ahmed (bin Muhammad bin Mughira) key hain. (jabkey Imam Nasai key dusrey ustaad Kasir bin Ubaid ney isey maaney ke sath riwayat kiya hai.)"
3095,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke jab Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un (zakaat na dene walon) sey ladaai karney ka azm (pakka irada) kar liya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Abu-Bakar ! aap un logon sey kaisey lad saktey hain jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farmane-giraami hai : mujhey logon sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh len. chunaanche jab wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh len to unhoney apney khoon aur maal mujh sey bacha liye magar ye ke un par kisi ka haq banta ho. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main us shakhs sey zarur ladunga jo namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq (farq) kerega (yani namaz padheyga magar Zakat na dega). Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey bakri ka eik bachcha bhi na den jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is baat par bhi un sey ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey malum ho gaya hai ke Allah Taala ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina un logon sey ladaai key liye khol diya hai. aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke ye baat bilkul sahih hai.
3096,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala ko piyarey ho gaey to bahut sey Arab murtad ho gaey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Abu-Bakar ! aap in Arbon sey kis buniyad par ladengey? Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladaai jari rakhun yahan tak ke wo gawahi dey den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah Taala ka Rasool hun aur namaz qaaim karen aur Zakat ada karen. Allah ki qism ! agar wo bakri ka eik bachcha bhi rok len jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein diya kartey they to main is par bhi un sey ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab mainey Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki raey par ghor kiya (aur dekha ke) unka Sina Allah ki taraf sey khol diya gaya hai, to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke yehi baat bar-haq hai. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke raawi Imran Qataan ilme hadees mein qawi nahin aur ye hadees (sanad key lihaz sey) ghalat hai. sahih riwayat pehli (3o93, 3094) hai, yani (زھری an عبیداللہ بن عبداللہ بن عتبۃ an أبی ھریرہ)."
3097,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney batlaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey logon sey ladney ko kaha gaya hai yahan tak ke wo (لاَ اِلَہَ أِلاَّ اللّٰہ ) padh li. jis shakhs ney ye padh liya, us ney mujh sey apna jaan aur maal bacha liya, albatta usey huquq deney padengey. haan ! us ka haqeeqi hisab Allah Taala ki zimme-daari hai."
3098,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mushrekin key sath apney maalon, haathon aur apni zabanon key sath jihad karo."
3099,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is haal mein faut huwa ke wo kabhi jihad ko nahin gaya, na kabhi jihad ki khahish ki, to wo nifaq key eik shobey par mara."
3100,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar ye baat na hoti ke bahut sey momin mujh sey peechhey rehna gawara nahin kerengey, aur mujh mein itni taqat nahin ke main un sab ko sawariyan (aur samane-jang) mohaiyya kar sakun, to main kisi lashkar sey peechhey na rehta jo Allah key raastey mein jihad karney jata. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! meri khahish hai ke main Allah key raastey mein shaheed kiya jaaun, phir zinda kiya jaaun, phir shaheed kiya jaaun, phir zinda kiya jaaun, phir shaheed kiya jaaun, phir zinda kiya jaaun, phir shaheed kiya jaaun."
3101,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Marwan bin Hakam ko bethey dekha to main bhi aa kar unkey paas beth gaya. unhoney hamein Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par ye aayat utri : (لاَ یَسْتَوِی الْقٰعِدُوْنَ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَالْمُجَاھِدُوْنَ فِیْ سَبِیْلِ اللّٰہِ),''gharon mein bethey rehney waley momin aur Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karney waley barabar nahin ho saktey.'' to Hazrat ibne Ummey Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aaye jab ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye aayat mujhey likhwa rahey they. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar main jihad karney ki taqat rakhta to main zarur jihad karta. Allah ne ye alfaz utaar diye : (غَیْرُ اُولِی الضَّرَرِ),''ba-sharte ke wo mazoor na hon.'' us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki raan mubarak meri raan par thi (wahi ki haalat ki wajeh sey) mujh par is qadr bojh pada ke mujhey khatra paida huwa ke meri raan toot jaeygi, phir aap sey wahi ki haalat khatam hui to aap ney ye alfaz padhey. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) farmatey hain ke ye Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq (sanad mein mazkur Imam Zohri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ka shagrid) moatabar hai, is mein koi kharabi nahin aur wo Abdur-Rehman bin Is-haq jis sey Ali bin Mus'hir, Abu Muawiya aur Abdul-Waahid bin Ziyad riwayat kartey hain aur wo khud Noman bin Saad sey bayan karta hai, qabile-bharosa aur moatabar nahin."
3102,"Hazrat Suhail bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Marwan ko masjid mein bethey dekha. main aaya aur unkey paas beth gaya, to unhoney hamein Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey ye aayat likhwaai : (لاَ یَسْتَوِی الْقٰعِدُوْنَ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَالْمُجَاھِدُوْنَ فِیْ سَبِیْلِ اللّٰہِ),''jihad ko na janey waley momin aur jihad karney waley momin barabar nahin ho saktey.''aap mujhey ye aayat likhwa rahey they ke us doran ibne Ummey Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aa gaey. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar mujh mein jihad ki taqat hoti to main zarur jihad karta. wo na-bina shakhs they, phir Allah Taala ney apney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par wahi utaari jab ke aap ki raan mubarak meri raan par thi (mujh par is qadr bojh pada ke) qarib tha meri raan toot jati. phir aap sey kaifiyate-wahi door hui to Allah Taala ney ye alfaz utarey they : (یْرُ اُولِی الضَّرَرِ),""ba-sharte ke wo (jihad sey peechey bethey rehney waley) mazoor na hon.''"
3103,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey paas kandhey ki haddi ya koi takhti laao, phir aap ney likhwaya : (لاَ یَسْتَوِی الْقٰعِدُوْنَ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَالْمُجَاھِدُوْنَ فِیْ سَبِیْلِ اللّٰہِ),''(jihad sey peechhey) bethey rehney waley momin aur jihad karney waley barabar nahi ho saktey.''Hazrat Amr ibne Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aap key peechhey bethey they. kehney lagey : (aey Allah key Nabi ! ) kya mujhey rukhsat (chhoot) hai? phir ye alfaz utrey : (غَیْرُ اُولِی الضَّرَرِ),""jo mazoor na hon."""
3104,"Hazrat Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab ye aayat utri : (لاَ یَسْتَوِی الْقٰعِدُوْنَ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَالْمُجَاھِدُوْنَ فِیْ سَبِیْلِ اللّٰہِ),''(jihad sey peechhey) bethey rehney waley momin (aur mujahideen) barabar nahin ho saktey.'' to Hazrat ibne Ummey Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) jo ke eik na-bina shakhs they, hazir huye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey barey mein kya hukm hai? jabkey main to na-bina hun (jihad nahin kar sakta) wo poochhtey rahey yahan tak ke ye alfaz utrey : (غَیْرُ اُولِی الضَّرَرِ),''ba-sharte ke wo mazoor na hon.''"
3105,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. wo aap sey jihad ki ijazat talab karta tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : terey waliden zinda hain? us ney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : phir to un ki khidmat kar. yehi jihad hai.
3106,Hazrat Muawiya bin Jahima Sulami sey riwayat hai ke (merey walid mohtaram) Hazrat Jahima (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool! mera irada jang ko janey ka hai jabkey main aap sey mashwara leney key liye hazir huwa hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teri walida hai? us ney kaha : ji haan! aap ney farmaya : uskey paas hi reh (aur khidmat kar). jannat uskey paaun taley hai.
3107,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! sab logon mein sey kon afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney nafs o maal key sath Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad kerey. us ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! phir kon ? aap ney farmaya : phir wo momin jo kisi pahadi wadi mein farokash ho gaya ho, Allah Taala sey darta ho aur logon ko apney shar sey mehfooz rakhta ho."
3108,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghazwa tabuk waley saal logon ko khutba irshad farma rahey they. aap ney apni sawari sey tek laga rakhi thi. aap ney farmaya : kya main tumhen behtareen aur bad-tareen insan key barey mein na bataun ? bilashuba behtareen insan wo hai jo Allah Taala key raastey mein ghodey par sawar ho kar ya oont par sawar ho kar ya pedal kaam karta rahey yahan tak ke usey maut aa jaey. aur beshak logon mein sab sey bura wo faajir shakhs hai jo Allah ki kitab padhta hai aur uski kuch parwa nahin karta.
3109,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jo shakhs Allah Taala key dar sey rotaa hai, usey aag nahin lagegi, yahan tak ke (doha huwa) doodh dobara pistaan mein chala jaey. aur ye nahin ho sakta ke kisi musalman key nathnon mein Allah key raastey mein (jihad kartey huye zamin sey udaney wala) ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan dono jama ho jaeyn."
3110,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo shakhs aag mein nahin jaeyga jo Allah key dar sey ro pada, yahan tak ke (doha huwa) doodh pistaan mein wapas chala jaey. aur dorane-jihad mein padney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan ikhattey nahin ho saktey."
3111,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mumkin nahin ke musalman us kafir key sath jahannam mein ikhatta ho jisey us ney qatl kya ho b-sharte-ke wo musalman baad mein durust raha aur shariyat par kar-band raha. aur Allah Taala key raastey mein ghubar aur jahannam ki haraarat kisi momin key pet mein jama nahin ho saktey. aur kisi momin key dil mein eman aur hasad jama nahin ho saktey.
3112,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey mein udney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan kisi momin key pet mein kabhi jama nahin hongey. isi tarah bukhl aur eman kabhi bhi kisi insan key dil mein jama nahin hongey.
3113,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey main udney wala ghubar aur Jahannam ka dhuwan kisi eik aadmi key chehrey mein kabhi jama nahin hongey. aur bukhl aur eman bhi kisi insan key dil mein jama nahin hotey
3114,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey ka ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan kisi aadmi key pet mein jama nahin ho saktey aur lalach aur eman kisi aadmi key pet mein jama nahin hotey
3115,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey mein padney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan kisi musalman key nathnon mein kabhi bhi jama nahin hongey.
3116,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey mein udney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan kisi musalman key nathnon mein jama nahin hongey aur bukhl aur eman kisi musalman aadmi key dil mein jama nahin hotey
3117,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Allah Taala apney raastey ka ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan kisi musalman key pet mein jama nahin farmaai ga. isi tarah Allah Taala kisi musalman aadmi key dil mein eman aur kanjusi ko jama nahin farmaeyga.
3118,"Hazrat Yazid bin abi Maryam bayan kartey hain ke main Juma key liye pedal ja raha tha ke mujhey Hazrat Abaya bin Raafey aa miley. kehney lagey : khush ho jaao kyonkey terey ye qadam Allah key raastey mein uth rahey hain aur mainey Hazrat abu-Abas (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key qadam Allah Taala key raastey mein ghubar aalud ho jaeyn, wo shakhs aag par haram hai."
3119,Hazrat Abu Rehana (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : wo aankh aag par haram kar di gaee hai jo Allah key raastey (jihad ) main bedaar rahey.
3120,Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key raastey main eik din subh ya Sham key waqt jana duniya aur uski har chiz sey afzal hai.
3121,Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik din subh ya Sham key waqt Allah Taala key raastey mein jana (duniya ki) har us chiz sey behtar hai jis par suraj tulu ya ghurub hota hai.
3122,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs aisey hain ke un mein sey har eik ki madad karna Allah Taala par zaroori hai : Allah key raastey mein jihad karney wala, wo nikah karney wala jo gunah sey bachna chahta hai aur wo ghulam jisney apney Malik sey azadi ka muahida kar rakha hai aur uski niyat muahida pura karney ki hai."
3123,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen shakhs Allah Taala key khususi mehman hain : jang ko janey wala, Haj ko janey wala aur Umerey ko janey wala."
3124,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala us shakhs key liye jo uskey raastey mein jihad karney jata hai aur uskey janey ka wahid maqsad Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad aur uskey Deen ki tasdeeq o taeed karna hai, is baat ka zaamin hai ke ( agar wo shaheed ho gaya to) usey zarur jannat mein dakhil kerega ya (agar wo zinda raha to) usey uskey ghar mein, jahan sey wo gaya tha, wapis pahunchaeyga, neez usey ajr aur ghanimat bhi hasil hongey."
3125,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala ney us shakhs key liye jo jihad key liye nikalta hai, us baat ki zamanat li hai ke usey main har haal mein jannat mein dakhil karunga, chahey wo jang mein qatl ho ya bistar par faut ho ya main usey us ghar mein wapis laaunga jahan sey wo nikla tha, qata nazar us ajr ya ghanimat key jo wo hasil karey b-sharte-ke jihad par usey nikalney wali chiz sirf mujh par eman aur meri raah mein jihad karney ka jazba ho."
3126,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karney waley ki misal us shakhs ki tarah hai jo musalsal qiyam o siyam mein mashghool rahey. wesay Allah hi behtar janta hai kon uskey raastey mein jihad karta hai (aur kon dunyawi aghraz key liye). aur Allah Taala apney raastey mein jihad karney waley key liye zaamin hai ke usey faut kerega to jannat mein dakhil kerega ya usey sahih Salim ajr o ghanimat samet uskey ghar wapis lotayega.
3127,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo bhi lashkar Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad ko jaey aur ghanimat hasil karey to wo apney ukhrawi ajr ka do tihai fauran hasil kar leta hai aur eik tihai ajr uskey liye baqi reh jata hai, lekin agar wo ghanimat hasil na karey to usey us ka pura pura sawab milega."
3128,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney rab Jaleel sey bayan farmaya : mera jo banda bhi meri raza mandi key husool key liye jihad fi sabilillah mein nikla, main usey zamanat deta hun ke usey ajr ya ghanimat key sath ghar wapis karunga. aur agar mainey uski jaan qabz kar li to uskey sab gunah maaf kar dunga aur is par khususi rehmat farmaunga."
3129,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karney waley ki misal aur Allah Taala hi khub janta hai ke kon Allah key raastey mein jihad karta hai, us shakhs ki tarah hai jo musalsal siyaam o qiyam karta rahey aur khushu o khuzoo key sath rukoo o sajda karta rahey."
3130,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir ho kar kehney laga : mujhey koi aisa amal bataiye jo jihad key barabar ho. aap ney farmaya : main to koi aisa kaam (qabile-amal) nahin paata. kya to is baat ki taqat rakhta hai ke jab sey Mujahid ( jihad key liye ghar sey) nikley , to masjid mein dakhil ho jaey aur namaz shuru kar dey (aur uski wapsi tak ) zarra bhar susti na kerey. neez rozey rakhna shuru kar dey aur kuch na khaye piye ? us shakhs ney kaha : iski kon taqat rakh sakta hai?"
3131,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha ke kon sa amal behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala par eman lana aur Allah azz-w-jall key raastey mein jihad karna.
3132,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : kon sa amal afzal hai? farmaya : Allah Taala par eman lana. usney arz kya : phir kon sa? aap ney farmaya : Allah key raastey mein jihad karna. us ney arz kya ke phir kon-sa? aap ney farmaya : Allah ki bargah mein maqbool hajj.
3133,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey abu-Saeed ! jo shakhs Allah Taala ki ruboobiyat, deene-Islam aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki nabuwat par (dil o jaan sey) razi ho gaya, uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee. Hazrat abu-Saeed ko ye kalmaat badey ajeeb lagey. wo kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool! ye kalmaat dobara irshad farmaiye : aap ney dobara irshad farmaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aur chiz hai ke Allah Taala iski wajeh sey us shakhs ko jannat mein so darjey buland farmaeyga. har do darjon key darmiyan aasman o zamin key maa-bain fasla hai. abu-Saeed ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo kon si chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karna. Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karna."
3134,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs namaz qaaim kerey. Zakat ada karey aur us haal mein marey ke Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek na thehrata ho to Allah Taala par lazim hai ke uski bakhshish farmaey, chahey wo hijrat karey ya apni paidaish hi key ilaqey mein faut ho jaey. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya hum ye baat logon ko na bata den ke wo khush ho jaeyn ? aap ney farmaya : jannat mein so darjey hain. har do darjon key darmiyan aasman o zamin key maa-bain key barabar fasla hai. Allah Taala ney wo darjey uski raah mein jihad karney walon key liye tayyar kar rakhey hain. aur agar ye khatra na hota ke main musalmanon par mashaqqat dal bethunga aur main itni sawariyan (aur wasaail) nahin paata ke main unhen sawariyan mohaiyya kar sakun aur unhen ye baat hergiz gawara na hogi ke merey peechey bethey rahen, to main kisi lashkar sey peechey na rehta. aur meri khahish hai ke main shaheed kya jaaun, phir zinda kya jaaun. phir shaheed kya jaaun."
3135,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid Raziallahu anhu farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs mujh par eman laya, musalman (mutee) huwa aur usney hijrat ki, main uskey liye jannat key kinarey main eik ghar aur jannat key darmiyan main eik ghar ka zaamin hun. aur jo shakhs mujh par eman laya, musalman (mutee) huwa aur Allah Taala key raastey mein usney jihad kya, main uskey liye jannat key kinarey main eik ghar, jannat key darmiyan main eik ghar aur jannat key intehai buland hissey main eik ghar ka zaamin hun. jis shakhs ney ye kaam kiye, usney khair hasil karney ka koi moqey aur shar sey bhagney ka koi moqey na chhoda. wo jahan marzi faut ho."
3136,"Hazrat Sabra bin Abu Faka (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : shetan insan ( ko gumrah karney key liye us ) key sab raaston par bethta hai. wo us ( ko gumrah karney ) key liye Islam key raastey par bethta hai aur kehta hai : kya to Islam la kar apney aur apney aaba-w ijdaad key Deen ko chhod dega? lekin insan uski nafarmani karkey musalman ho jata hai. phir wo uskey samney hijrat key raastey par beth jata hai aur kehta hai : kya to hijrat kar key apna watan aur aasman chhod dega ? jab ke muhaajir ki misal to aisey hai jaisey ghoda rassi key sath baandh diya gaya ho. lekin insan uski nafarmani karta hai aur hijrat kar leta hai. phir shetan uskey samney jihad key raastey par aa kar bethta hai aur kehta hai ke to jihad kerega? ye to jaan o maal ki mashaqqat ka naam hai. phir to ladaai kerega. to maara jaeyga. teri aurat sey koi doosra shakhs shaadi kar lega. aur tera maal warison mein taqseem kar diya jaeyga. lekin momin uski nafarmani karta hai aur jihad karta hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs ye sab kuch karey to Allah Taala par lazim ho jata hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil farmaey, aur jo shaheed ho jaey to phir bhi Allah Taala par lazim ho jata hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil farmaai aur agar wo gharq ho jaey to bhi Allah Taala par lazim ho jata hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil farmaey. aur agar us (ki sawari) ka janwer usko gira kar uski gardan tod dey to bhi Allah Taala par lazim ho jata hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil farmaey."
3137,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah key raastey mein joda ( joda ) kharch kerey. usey jannat mein bulaya jaeyga : aey Allah key bandey ! ye bahut behtar hai (idhar aao). jo shakhs ( nafl ) namaz ka aadi hoga usey namaz waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga aur jo shakhs jihad ka shoqin hoga, usey jihad waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga aur jo shakhs (nafl) sadqaat mein maroof hoga, usey sadqey waley darwazey sey aawaz di jaeygi aur jo shakhs ( nafl ) rozon ka aadi hoga, usey sairabi waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : aey Allah key Nabi ! kisi shakhs ko zarurat to nahin ke usey jannat key sab darwazon sey bulaya jaey lekin kya koi aisa bhi hoga jisey sab darwazon sey bulaya jaeyga ? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur mujhey ummid hai ke to un mein sey hoga."
3138,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik Erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : eik aadmi shohrat key liye ladaai karta hai ya ghanimat hasil karney key liye ladta hai ya apna martaba zahir karney key liye ladaai ladta hai, un mein sey Allah key raastey mein kon hai? aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs is liye ladaai karta hai ke Allah Taala ka kalma buland ho to wohi Allah Taala key raastey mein hai."
3139,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar bayan kartey hain ke log Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey uth kar chaley gaey to Sham walon mein sey naatal naami eik shakhs ney kaha : buzurgwar mohtaram! mujhey koi aisi hadees bayan kijiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho. unhoney kaha : theek hai. mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : sab sey pehley jinka faisla qiyamat key din kya jaeyga, teen ashkhas hongey : eik wo aadmi jo shaheed huwa. usey laya jaeyga. Allah Taala usey apney ehsanat ginwaaeyga. wo unhen taslim kerega. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tuney un nematon key badley mein kya kaam kya? wo kahega : mainey terey raastey mein jihad kya yahan tak ke shaheed ho gaya. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot bola. to to is liye lada tha ke kaha jaey : falan shakhs bahut bahaadur hai. ye baat (duniya mein) bahut keh di gaee, phir hukm diya jaeyga aur usey chehrey key bal ghaseet kar aag mein phenk diya jaeyga. doosra wo shakhs jisney ilm seekha aur sikhaya aur Quran Majeed padha. usey bhi laya jaeyga. Allah Taala usey apney ehsanat ginwaaeyga. wo un sab ka aetraaf kerega. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tuney un nematon key badley mein kya kya? wo kahega : mainey ilm seekha aur sikhaya. aur teri raza mandi key liye Quran padha. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tuney jhoot bola. tuney to isliye ilm seekha tha ke tujhey aalim kaha jaey aur Quran isliye padha tha ke tujhey qaari kaha jaey. ye sab kuch to keh diya gaya. uskey barey mein bhi hukm diya jaeyga aur usey chehrey key bal ghaseet kar aag mein dal diya jaeyga. aur teesra wo shakhs ke Allah Taala ney is par wusat farmaai aur usey har qism ka maal diya. usey bhi laya jaeyga. Allah Taala usey apni nematen yad dilaaeyga, wo unhen taslim kerega. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney un nematon key badley mein kya kya ? wo kahega : mainey koi aisi jagah nahin chhodi jahan to pasand karta ho. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) kehtey hain ke main (apney ustaad sey) « تُحِبُّ » ka lafz is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah main chahta tha … … ke kharch kya jaey magar mainey teri raza mandi key liye us jagah kharch kya. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney jhoot bola, balke tu ney ye sab kuch isliye kya ke log kahin ke ye bahut bada sakhi hai. ye baat to ( duniya mein) keh di gaee, phir uskey barey mein bhi hukm diya jaeyga aur usey chehrey key bal ghaseet kar aag mein phenk diya jaeyga."
3140,Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah key raastey mein jihad karney gaya lekin uski niyat sirf dunyawi maal hasil karna tha to usey uski niyat hi key mutabiq milega.
3141,Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs oont ka ghutna baandhney wali rassi hasil karney key liye jihad kerega to usey uski niyat key mutabiq hi milega.
3142,"Hazrat abu-Umama Bahili (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga : aap farmaeyn, eik shakhs jang ko jata hai. sawab aur shohrat dono ka talabgar hai. usey kya milega? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey kuch nahin milega. us shakhs ney ye sawal teen dafa dohraya. har dafa aap farmatey they : usey kuch nahin milega. phir aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala sirf us amal ko qubul farmata hai jo khalis uskey liye kya jaey aur sirf uski raza mandi maqsud ho."
3143,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo musalman aadmi Allah Taala key raastey mein oontni dohney key darmiyani waqfey key barabar ladaai kerey. uskey liye jannat wajib ho jaeygi. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala sey sachchey dil key sath shahadat ka sawal kerey. phir chahey faut ho jaey ya maara jaey, usey shaheed ka sawab milega. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein zakhmi ho gaya ya usey koi chot lagi to qiyamat key din us sey tezi sey khoon beh raha hoga. rang to zafraan jaisa hoga magar khushbu kastoori jaisi. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein zakhmi huwa, is par shahidon wali mehar lagi hogi."
3144,"Hazrat Sharjeel bin Samt ney Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aey Amr ! hamen koi aisi hadees bayan farmaain jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho. unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jis shakhs key baal Allah Taala key raastey mein safed ho gaey to wo safed baal uskey liye qiyamat key din Noor ka zaria ban jaeyngey. aur jis shakhs ney Allah Taala key raastey mein teer phenka, wo dushman tak pahunchey ya na pahunchey, uskey liye ghulam azad karney key barabar hoga. aur jo shakhs momin ghulam azad karey to us ka har uzu uskey har uzu key liye aag sey azadi ka sabab ban jaeyga."
3145,"Hazrat abu Najeeh Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jisney Allah key raastey main eik teer (dushman tak ) pahunchaya, usey jannat main eik darja hasil ho jaeyga, mainey us din sola teer dushmanon tak pahunchaey, neez mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein teer chalaey to usey ghulam key azad karney key barabar sawab milega."
3146,"Hazrat Sharjeel bin Samt ney Hazrat Kaab bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aey Kaab ! hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey koi hadees bayan farmaain aur is silsiley mein puri ehtiyat farmaain (ke hadees mein koi kami-beshi na ho.) unhoney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jis aadmi key baal Islam mein Allah key raastey mein safed ho gaey, wo uskey liye qiyamat key din Noor ban jaeyngey. unhoney phir kaha : hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik aur hadees bayan farmaai aur puri-puri ehtiyat farmaai (ke kami beshi na ho.) unhoney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : teerandazi kya karo. jo shakhs dushman tak teer pahunchaey, Allah Taala uski wajeh sey uska eik darja buland farmaeyga. (ye sun kar) Hazrat ibn Naham (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! darjey sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : wo darja teri maa key ghar ki chaukhat key barabar nahin balke (jannat key) do darjon key darmiyan so saal ka fasla hai."
3147,"Hazrat Sharjeel bin Samt sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aey Amr ! hamen koi hadees bayan farmaiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho. is mein koi bhool chook ya kami na ho. unhoney kaha ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna, jisney Allah Taala key raastey mein teer chalaya aur dushman tak pahuncha diya, (woh terey dushman ko) laga ya na laga, wo uskey liye eik ghulam ki azadi ki tarah hoga. aur jis shakhs ney koi musalman ghulam azad kya to us ka har uzu uskey har uzu key badley mein jahannam ki aag sey azad hoga. aur jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein ( kaam karta karta ) boodha ho gaya to uskey safed baal qiyamat key din uskey liye Noor ban jaeyngey."
3148,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala eik teer ki wajeh sey teen ashkhas ko jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga : bananey wala, jo usey banatey waqt neki ka zehen rakhta hai, teer phainkney wala aur teer pakdaaney wala."
3149,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein zakhmii hota hai … aur Allah Taala hi behtar janta hai ke kon Allah Taala ki raah mein zakhmii hota hai … to wo qiyamat key din is haalat mein aayega ke uskey zakham sey khoon tezi sey beh raha hoga. rang to khoon ka hoga magar khushbu kastoori ki hogi.
3150,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Solba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( shohdaaey ahad key barey mein) farmaya tha : unhen unkey khoon ( aalud jism aur kapdon ) samet dhanp kar dafn kar do kyonkey jo zakham bhi Allah Taala key raastey mein lagta hai, wo qiyamat key din us haalat mein hoga ke us sey khoon beh raha hoga. rang to khoon ka hoga magar khushbu kastoori ki hogi."
3151,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : jab Uhad ka din tha aur log bhag khadey huye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) baara ansariyon key gherey mein (maidan key) eik kinarey mein (datey huye) they. un mein (eik muhaajir ) Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mojud they. mushrikon ney unhen ghera to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sathiyon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : kon un dushmanon ka muqabla kerega ? Hazrat Talha ney kaha : main. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to jis jagah hai wahin thehra reh. eik Ansari ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main muqabla karta hun. farmaya : han, to muqabla kar. us ney ladaai ki yahan tak ke wo shaheed ho gaya. aap ney phir tawajjoh farmaai to mushrik abhi tak mojud they. aap ney farmaya : kon dushmanon ka muqabla kerega? Hazrat Talha ney kaha : main. aap ney farmaya : to jahan hai wahin reh. eik aur Ansari ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main. farmaya : han, to muqabla kar. us ney ladaai ladi yahan tak ke wo bhi shaheed ho gaya. aap barabar yehi farmatey rahey aur eik eik Ansari nikalta raha aur apney pesh-rau ki tarah ladaai karta raha aur shaheed hota raha yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah (Raziallahu anhu) hi baqi reh gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney phir farmaya : kon dushmanon ka muqabla kerega ? Hazrat Talha ney kaha : main kya karunga. aur unhoney ladaai shuru kar di. aur wo apney pesh-rau giyara ansariyon ki tarah ladey yahan tak ke unkey haath par talwaar lagi aur ungliyan kat gaeen. to unkey munh sey «حَسَّ » ( اوئی waghera ) nikla. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ( jab tujhey zakham laga tha ) agar to «Bismillah» kehta to tujhey farishtey utha letey. aur log dekhtey rehtey. phir Allah Taala ney mushrikon ko pher diya."
3152,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jab khaibar ki ladaai hui to merey bhai ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath mein khub ladaai ki, phir un ki talwaar mud kar unhi ko lagi aur wo Allah ko piyarey ho gaey. kuch as-haab Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us barey mein chemegoiyan kin aur unki shahadat key barey mein shak kya (aur kaha) ke ye aadmi to apney hathiyar sey mara hai. Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar sey wapsi ka safar shuru farmaya to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap mujhey ijazat detey hain ke main aap ki mojudgi mein kuch ashaar padh lun ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ijazat marahmat farmaai. Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jo kehna hai ghor sey kehna (koi sher khilaf shara na ho). mainey ye sher padhey : ""Allah ki qasam! agar Allah Taala ki rehmat na hoti to hum hidayat na paatey"" na sadqey kartey, na namazein padhtey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tuney sahih kaha. ( phir padha : ) ( فَأَنزِ لَنْ سَکِیْنَۃً … وَالْمُشْرِکُوْنَ قَدْ بَغَوْا عَلَیْنَا ) ""aey Allah ! hum par sukoon o itminan nazil farma aur agar dushman sey muqabla ho to hamen sabit qadam rakhna, mushrikon ney hum par zulm o sitam kiye hain."" jab mainey apney sher purey kiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye sher kis ney kahey hain? mainey kaha : merey bhai ney. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah is par reham farmaey. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! kuch log uskey liye duaaey maghfirat karney sey dartey hain. wo kehtey hain ke ye shakhs to apney hathiyar sey mara hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo to badi koshish sey jihad kartey huye Allah ko piyaara huwa hai. ( hadees key raawi ) ibne-Shahab (Imam Zohri ) ney kaha ke mainey Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) key betey sey puchha to usney apney baap sey usi (mazkura hadees ki ) tarah hadees bayan ki lekin ye baat ziyada kahi ke jab main ( Salma bin Akwa ) ney kaha ke log uskey liye duaaey maghfirat karney sey dartey they. to (ye sun kar) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ney ghalat kya, wo to badi koshish sey jihad kartey huye mara hai. usey dugna ajr milega. (ye farmatey huye ) aap ney apni do ungliyon sey ishara farmaya."
3153,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye khatra na hota ke main apni ummat par mashaqqat dal dunga to main kisi lashkar sey peechey na rehta, lekin wo sawari key janwer nahin paatey aur main bhi itney janwer nahin paata ke un sab ko sawari mohaiyya kar sakun. aur mujh sey peechey rehna un par shaaq guzartaa hai. meri khahish hai ke main Allah Taala key raastey mein shaheed kya jaaun, phir zinda kya jaaun, phir shaheed kya jaaun, phir zinda kya jaaun, phir shaheed kya jaun. teen dafa farmaya."
3154,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar ye khadsha na hota ke momin mujh sey peechey rehna gawara nahin kerengey, aur main itni sawariyan nahin paata ke un sab ko sawar kar sakun, to main jihad fi-sabilillah key janey waley kisi lashkar sey bhi peechey na rehta. qism us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! meri khahish hai ke main Allah Taala key raastey mein shaheed ho jaaun, phir zinda kya jaaun, phir shaheed ho jaaun, phir zinda kya jaaun, phir shaheed ho jaaun."
3155,"Hazrat ibn abi Umera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi bhi musalman shakhs jisey us ka rab taala apney paas bula ley, ye khahish nahin kerega ke wo tumharey paas ( duniya mein) wapis aa jaey, chahey usey duniya ki har chiz mil jaey, magar shaheed wapsi ki khahish kerega. ibn abi Umera (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey Allah Taala key raastey mein shaheed hona us baat sey ziyada pasand hai ke sab badwi aur shahri merey ghulam ban jaeyn."
3156,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jange-Uhad key din eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha ke aap mujhey bataeyn, agar main Allah Taala key raastey mein maara jaaun to main kahan jaaunga? (aap ney ) farmaya : jannat mein. us ney apney haath mein pakdi hui khajuren (jinhen wo kha raha tha ) phenk den aur ( kafiron sey) ladney laga yahan tak ke shaheed ho gaya."
3157,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa jabkey aap member par khutba irshad farma rahey they. wo kehney laga : aap farmaain agar main Allah Taala key raastey mein sabit qadmi sey ladtaa huwa maara jaaun jab ke meri niyat bhi sawab hi ki ho, rukh maidane-jang ki taraf ho, peeth na ho, to kya Allah Taala merey sab gunah maaf farma dega? aap ney farmaya : han, phir aap kuchh der khamosh rahey. phir farmaya : wo shakhs kidhar hai jisney abhi sawal kiya tha? us aadmi ney kaha : main ye khada hun. aap ney farmaya : tuney kya kaha tha? us ney kaha : agar main Allah Taala key raastey mein sabit qadmi sey ladtaa huwa maara jaaun jab ke meri niyat bhi sawab ki ho. mera rukh dushman ki taraf ho na ke peeth, to kya Allah Taala merey tamam gunah maaf farma dega? aap ney farmaya : han, lekin qarz (kisi ka wajibul-adaa haq maaf na hoga). Jibril alehissalam ney ye baat mujhey abhi chupkey sey batai hai."
3158,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaain agar main Allah Taala key raastey mein sabit qadmi key sath ladtaa huwa shaheed ho jaaun. meri niyat bhi sawab ki ho. maidane-jang sey munh bhi na modoon to kya Allah Taala meri tamam ghaltiyaan maaf farma dega? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haan. jab wo shakhs wapis chala to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aawaz di, ya aap ney kisi ko hukm diya aur usey aawaz di gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tuney kaisey kaha tha? us ney apni puri baat dohra di to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : theek hai magar qarz (ya kisi ka wajibul-adaa haq) maaf nahin hoga. Jibril alehissalam ney mujhey aisey hi kaha hai."
3159,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutbey key liye khadey huye aur zikr farmaya ke Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad aur Allah Taala par eman sab kamon sey afzal kaam hain. eik aadmi khada huwa aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaain agar main Allah Taala key raastey mein maara jaaun to kya Allah Taala meri ghaltiyaan maaf farma dega? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : han, ba-sharte-ke to Allah Taala key raastey mein is haal mein maara jaey ke to sabr ka muzahira karey aur teri niyat sawab ki ho. to dushman ki taraf badh raha ho, peeth pher kar bhag na raha ho, magar qarz (kisi ka wajibul-adaa haq) maaf na hoga. Jibril alehissalam ney mujhey ye baat kahi hai."
3160,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap member par ( khutba irshad farma rahey ) they. wo kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap farmaiye agar main apni is talwaar key sath Allah key raastey mein sabit qadmi key sath ladaai ladun jab ke meri niyat bhi sawab hasil karney ki ho, munh dushman ki taraf ho na ke peeth, yahan tak ke main maara jaaun, to kya Allah Taala meri ghaltiyaan maaf farma dega? aap ney farmaya : haan. jab wo janey key liye muda to aap ney usey bulaya aur farmaya : ye Jibril alehissalam farma rahey hain ke ghaltiyaan to maaf ho jaeyngi lekin terey zimmey wajibul-adaa huquq huye to wo maaf nahin hongey."
3161,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zamin par rehney wala jo bhi shakhs faut ho aur uskey liye Allah Taala key yahan khair ho, wo ye pasand nahin kerega ke tumharey paas wapis aa jaey, chahey usey sari duniya hi mil jaey, magar shaheed khahish kerega ke wapis (duniya mein) aaye aur dobara shaheed ho."
3162,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jannat walon mein sey eik shakhs ko laya jaeyga. Allah Taala us sey farmaeyga : aey Adam key betey ! tu ney apney jannati ghar ko kaisa paya? wo kahega : ya Allah ! behtareen ghar. Allah Taala farmaeyga : mang jo tamanna hai. wo kahega : main ye maangta hun ke to mujhey duniya mein wapis bhej dey taake main terey raastey mein das dafa qatl kya jaaun. aur ye us bina par ke wo shahadat ki fazilat dekh lega.
3163,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shaheed shahadat key waqt takleef mehsus nahin karta magar itni jo tum mein sey koi shakhs kisi key chutki kaatney sey mehsus karta hai.
3164,"Hazrat Sahal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sachchey dil key sath Allah Taala sey shahadat maangeyga, Allah Taala usey shohda key martabey tak pahunchaeyga agar-che wo apney bistar par faut ho."
3165,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch haalaten aisi hain ke jo shakhs bhi in mein faut ho wo shaheed hoga : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. jo Allah Taala key raastey mein gharq ho, wo shaheed hai. jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein pet ki takleef sey mar jaey, wo shaheed hai. jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein taaoon sey mar jaey, wo shaheed hai. aur jo aurat Allah Taala key raastey mein zachgi sey mar-jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai."
3166,"Hazrat Arbaaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : shaheed aur bistaron par faut honey waley, taaoon sey faut honey walon key barey mein Allah Taala key samney jhagda kerengey. shuhda kahengey : ye hamarey bhai hain kyonkey ye bhi hamari tarah qatl hi huye hain. aur bistaron par faut honey waley kahengey : ye hamarey bhai hain kyonkey ye hamari tarah bistaron par faut huye hain. Rab taala farmaeyga : unkey zakham dekho. agar unkey zakham maqtooleen key zakhmon ki tarah hain to ye un mein shumar hongey aur unkey sath rahengey. jab dekha jaeyga to unkey zakham shuhda key zakhmon jaisey hongey."
3167,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala do aadmiyon sey tajjub karta hai aur raawi ney dusri baar kaha : hansta hai ke un mein sey eik dusrey ko qatl karta hai, phir dono jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain."
3168,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala do aadmiyon ko dekh kar hanstaa hai jin mein sey eik dusrey ko qatl karta hai, phir dono jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain. ( un mein sey) eik shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein ladaai karta hai aur maara jata hai, phir Allah Taala qatil ki tauba qubul farmata hai. ( wo musalman ho jata hai) aur wo Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad karta hai aur shaheed kar diya jata hai."
3169,"Hazrat Salman khair (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs jang key liye tayyar ho kar eik din raat key liye sarhad par betha rahey, usey eik maah key rozon aur namaz ka sawab milega. aur jo sarhad par betha betha faut ho jaey, uskey liye mazkura sawab jari rakha jaeyga aur us ka rizq bhi jari rakha jaeyga aur wo imtihan leney walon sey mehfooz rahega."
3170,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs jihad key liye eik din raat sarhad par tayyar ho kar baitha, usey eik mahiney key siyaam o qiyam (namaz-rozey) ka sawab milega. aur jisey sarhad par bethey-bethey maut aa gaee, uskey liye uska ye nek amal jari rakha jaeyga. wo imtihan leney walon sey mehfooz rahega aur uska rizq jari rakha jaeyga."
3171,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : Allah Taala key rastey main eik din sarhad par tayyar ho kar bethna ( neki key) dusrey maqamat mein hazar din bethney sey afzal hai.
3172,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jihad main eik din kharch karna (neki key) dusrey kamon mein hazar din laganey sey behtar hai.
3173,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab quba ko jatey to Hazrat Umme-Haraam binte-Milhan (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bhi jatey they. wo aap ko khana kehlati thin. aur Umme-Haraam binte-Milhan Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi thin. eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif ley gaey to unhoney aapko khana khilaya, phir wo beth kar aap key sar mein juein talash karney lagin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) so gaey. phir jaagey to aap hans rahey they. Umme-Haraam kehti hain : mainey kaha aey Allah key Rasool ! kon si chiz aap ko hansa rahi hai? aap ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuch log Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad ko jatey huye mujhey dikhlaaye gaey jo samandar ki mojon par sawar ja rahey they, jabkey wo takhton par badshah baney bethey hain ya (yun farmaya :) jaisey takhton par badshah bethey hotey hain. Is-haq (raawi) ko shak hai. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! Allah Taala sey dua karen ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi un mein shamil farmaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey liye dua farmaai, phir aap so gaey. Haris (raawi) ney kaha : phir aap so gaey, kuch der baad jaagey to muskura rahey they. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kis wajeh sey tabassum farma rahey hain? aap ney farmaya : meri ummat key kuch aur log mujh par pesh kiye gaey jo Allah key raastey mein ( samandar par sawar ) jihad ko ja rahey hain jo takhton par badshah baney bethey hain ya ( yun farmaya : ) jaisey takhton par badshah bethey hain. jaisey aap ney pehley farmaya tha. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! dua keren, Allah Taala mujhey un mein shamil farmaey, aap ney farmaya : tum pehley lashkar mein shamil hogi. (aap ki is pesh-goi key mutabiq ) wo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key daur mein samandari jihad mein (apney khawind mohtaram key sath ) gaeen. jab wo samandar sey niklin to apni sawari key janwer sey gir padin aur Allah ko piyari ho gaeen."
3174,"Hazrat Umme-Haraam binte-Milhan (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur qailula farmaya. aap jaagey to hans rahey they. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa-baap aap par qurban hun, aap ko kis chiz ney hansaaya? aap ney farmaya : mainey ( khuwab mein) apni ummat key kuch log dekhey jo samandari lashkar mein ja rahey hain jaisey takht par badshah bethey huye hain. mainey guzarish ki : aap dua farmaiye ke Allah Taala mujhey un mein shamil farmaey. aap ney farmaya : bilashuba tum un mein sey hogi. aap phir so gaey, phir jaagey to hans rahey they. mainey puchha, to aap ney isi tarah farmaya jis tarah pehley farmaya tha. mainey guzarish ki : dua keren, Allah Taala mujhey un mein shamil farmaey. aap ney farmaya : tum pehley lashkar mein shamil hogi. phir Hazrat Umme-Haraam sey Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ney nikah kar liya. wo bahrii lashkar mein gaey to ye bhi unkey sath gaeen. chunanche jab wo samandar sey niklin to eik khachar laya gaya. wo is par sawar honey lagin to usney unhen gira diya jis sey unki gardan toot gaee."
3175,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen ghazwa hind ki peshgoi farmaey. agar mainey us ghazwey ko pa liya to is mein apna jaan o maal sirf kar dunga, phir agar main is mein maara gaya to main afzal shuda mein shumar hunga aur agar zinda wapis aa gaya to phir main (aap ki peshgoi key mutabiq aag sey) azad Abu-Hurera hunga."
3176,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Hindustan par hamley ki peshgoi farmaai. agar mainey ye moqey pa liya to main is mein apna jaan o maal kharch karunga, phir agar main is mein shaheed ho gaya to main afzal shaheed hunga aur agar zinda wapis aa gaya to main (aag sey) azad Abu-Hurera hunga."
3177,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri ummat mein sey do jamaaton ko Allah Taala ney aag sey azad farma diya hai : eik wo jamaat jo Hindustan par hamla keregi aur dusri wo jamaat jo Hazrat Esa alehissalam key sath (mil kar dajjaal key muqabley mein saf ara) hogi.
3178,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khandaq khodney ka hukm diya to eik aisi chattan logon key samney aai jo logon aur (khandaq ki) khudaai key darmiyan rukawat ban gaee. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey, kudaal pakdi aur apni chadar khandaq key kinarey rakh di aur ye aayat padh kar zarab lagai : « { وَتَمَّتْ کَلِمَتُ رَبِّکَ صِدْقاً وَّعَدْلاً … وَھُوَالسَّمِیْعُ الْعَلِیْمُ }  aur puri hui terey rab ki baat sachai aur insaf key lihaz sey. koi uski baaton ko badalney wala nahin. aur wo khub sunney-janney wala hai. (aapki zarab sey) pathar ka teesra hissa ad gaya. Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) khadey dekh rahey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zarab key sath eik chamak paida hui. phir aap ney dobara zarab lagai aur wohi aayat padhi : « { وَتَمَّتْ کَلِمَتُ رَبِّکَ صِدْقاً وَّعَدْلاً … وَھُوَالسَّمِیْعُ الْعَلِیْمُ }  aur puri hui terey rab ki baat sidq o insaf key lihaz sey, koi uski baaton ko badalney wala nahin. aur wo khub sunney-janney wala hai. aur mazeed teesra hissa toot gaya, phir eik chamak paida hui jisey Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) ney dekha. phir aap ney teesri zarab lagai aur yehi aayat padhi : « { وَتَمَّتْ کَلِمَتُ رَبِّکَ صِدْقاً وَّعَدْلاً … وَھُوَالسَّمِیْعُ الْعَلِیْمُ }  aur puri hui terey rab ki baat sachai aur insaf key lihaz sey. koi uski baaton ko badalney wala nahin. aur wo khub sunney-janney wala hai. aur baqi pathar bhi reza-reza ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khandaq sey nikley, apni chadar uthai aur beth gaey. Salman (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool! jab aap zarbein laga rahey they to mainey aap ko dekha, jab bhi aap koi zarab lagatey they to uskey sath chamak paida hoti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : Salman! tu ney wo (chamak) dekhi thi? unhoney kaha : haan aey Allah key Rasool! qism us zaat ki jisney aapko bar-haq Nabi banaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey jab pehli zarab lagai thi to mujhey kisra key shehar aur ird-gird key bahut sey dusrey shehar dikhaye gaey yahan tak ke mainey unhen apni aakhon sey dekha. aap key paas mojud sahaba kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool! dua farmaain Allah Taala ye shehar hum par fatah farmaai aur unkey ghar hamen ghanimat mein inayat farmaey. aur hamarey haathon unkey ilaqey taraj farmaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye dua farmaai (aap ney farmaya : ) jab mainey phir dusri zarab lagai to mujhey qaisar aur ird-gird key bahut sey shehar dikhaye gaey yahan tak ke mainey unhen apni aakhon sey dekha. sahaba ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! dua farmaain ke Allah Taala ye ilaqey hamarey liye fatah farmaey. unkey ghar hamen ghanimat mein ata farmaai aur unkey ilaqey hamarey haathon taraj farmaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ye dua bhi farma di. (aap ney farmaya : ) phir mainey teesri zarab lagai to mujhey Habsha aur ird-gird key bahut sey shehar dikhlaaye gaey yahan tak ke mainey unhen apni aakhon sey dekha. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : habshiyon ko apney haal par rehney do jab tak wo tumhen tumharey haal par rehney den aur turkon ko kuch na kaho jab tak wo tumhen kuch na kahen."
3179,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahin hogi yahan tak ke musalman turkon sey ladaai ladengey. wo aisey log hongey jinkey chehrey chamda chadhai hui dhaalon ki tarah hongey. wo baalon key kapdey pahneingey aur baalon waley jootey pahneingey.
3180,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad sey riwayat hai ke merey walid mohtaram (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ) ney samjha ke shayad mujhey dusrey sahaba par fazilat hasil hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala kamzor logon ki duaon, namazon aur ikhlas ki wajeh sey is ummat ki madad farmata hai."
3181,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : merey paas kisi zaeef shakhs ko talash kar key laao, kyonkey un zaeef o kamzor logon ki wajeh sey tumhen rizq milta hai aur tumhari madad ki jati hai."
3182,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi jihad fi sabeelillah key liye kisi ghazi ko saman mohaiyya kerey. usney bhi jihad mein hissa liya. aur jo kisi ghazi ki ghair-mojudgi mein uskey ehal o ayal ki zarooriyat mohaiyya kerey. us ney bhi jihad kya.
3183,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi Mujahid fi sabililah ko samane-jang o safar mohaiyya kerey. us ney bhi jihad kya aur jo shakhs ghazi ki ghair-mojudgi mein uskey ehal o ayaal sey husne-suluk karey to us ney bhi jihad mein hissa liya.
3184,"Hazrat Ahnaf bin Qais sey riwayat hai ke hum Haj karney key liye nikley. hum Madina Munawra pahunchey. abhi hum apney apney maqamat mein saman utaar rahey they ke eik shakhs hamarey paas aaya aur kehney laga ke log masjide-nabwi mein jama hain aur wo ghabraey huye hain. hum masjid ko chaley to bahut sey log masjid key darmiyan mein kuch logon key ird-gird jama they. un mein hazraat Ali, Zuber, Talha aur Saad bin abi Waqas Raziallahu anhum bhi they. hum usi haal mein they ki Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aagey aur un par zard rang ki eik badi chadar thi. unhoney us sey sar ko dhanp rakha tha. wo farmaney lagey : kya yahan Talha hain, Zuber hain, Saad hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan. farmaney lagey : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs falan khandan ka khaliyian kharid (aur masjid key liye waqf ) kerega Allah Taala uskey sab gunah maaf kar dega. mainey bees ya pachchees hazar dirham sey usey kharida. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur aap ko ittilaa di. aap ney farmaya : ye hamari masjid mein shamil kar do. us ka sawab tumhen milega. un sab ney kaha : ji haan. Hazrat Usman ney farmaya : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : jo shakhs Rooma ka kunwaan kharid (kar waqf) kerega, Allah Taala uskey sab gunah maaf kar dega. mainey wo kunwaan itni itni ( Kasir ) raqam sey kharida. phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur arz kya ke mainey wo kunwaan itni raqam sey kharid liya hai. aap ney farmaya : usey aam musalmanon key peeney key liye waqf kar dey. is ka ajr tujhey milega. un sab ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! haan. phir Hazrat Usman ney kaha : main tumhen us Allah ki qism dey kar poochhta hun jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( ghazwa tabuk ki tayyari key waqt ) logon key chehron mein dekha aur farmaya : jo shakhs un … jaishe-Usra… ko samane-Harab o safar mohaiyya kerega, Allah Taala uskey sab gunah maaf kar dega. mainey unkey liye saman mohaiyya kya yahan tak ke unhen oont ka paaun baandhney wali kisi rassi ya oont ki mahaar ki bhi kami mehsus na hui? un sab logon ney kaha : Allah ki qasam! ji haan. Hazrat Usman kehney lagey : aey Allah gawah ho ja. aey Allah ! gawah ho ja. aey Allah ! gawah ho ja."
3185,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein joda kharch kerey. usey jannat mein aawazen di jaeyngi : aey Allah key bandey ! ye jagah achi hai (idhar aa jaao). jo shakhs (farz aur nafl) namaz ka shoqeen hoga, usey namaz waley darwazey sey bulaya jaeyga. jo shakhs jihad ka shoqin hoga, usey jihad waley darwazey sey aawaz di jaeygi. jo shakhs ( nafli) sadqaat mein maroof hoga, usey sadqey waley darwazey sey pukara jaeyga. aur jo shakhs ( naflii ) rozon ka aadi hoga, usey « بَابُ الرَّیَّان » ( sairaabii waley darwazey ) sey bulaya jaeyga. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : zarurat to nahin ke kisi shakhs ko un sab darwazon sey bulaya jaey magar kya kisi shakhs ko sab darwazon sey bulaya jaeyga? aap ney farmaya : haan. aur mujhey ummid hai ke to un mein sey hoga."
3186,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein joda kharch kerey. usey jannat key darbaan tamam darwazon sey bulaeyngey. aey falan ! idhar aao aur (yahan sey) dakhil ho jaao. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! us shakhs ko to kisi qism ka khasara nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ummid hai ke to bhi un mein sey hoga.
3187,Hazrat Sasaa bin Muawiya sey manqul hai ke main Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila. mainey arz kya ke mujhey koi hadees bayan karen. unhoney farmaya : zarur. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman banda apney har maal sey joda joda Allah Taala key raastey mein kharch kerey. usey jannat key darbaan milengey aur har darbaan usey apney darwazey mein sey guzarney ki dawat dega. mainey kaha joda kharch karney sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : agar uskey paas oont hain to do oont Allah key raastey mein dey aur agar uskey paas gayen hain to do gayen dey.
3188,Hazrat Khurem bin Faatik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein koi chiz kharch kerey. uskey liye usey saat so guna tak likha jata hai.
3189,Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Allah key raastey mein mahaar wali eik oontni sadqa ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din ye shakhs mahaar wali saat oontniyaan ley kar aayega.
3190,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jang do qism ki hoti hai. jo shakhs Allah ki raza mandi ka Talib ho, Imam ki itaat karey aur achcha maal kharch karey aur apney sathi sey narmi karey aur fasad sey bachey to us ka sona aur jaagna sab ka sab sawab hoga. lekin jo shakhs dikhawey aur shohrat key liye jang kerey. Imam ki nafarmani karey aur zamin mein fasad karey to wo apni pehli haalat key sath bhi wapis nahin aayega. (bhaley hi wo koi sawab hasil kerey)."
3191,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujahideen ki aurten jang mein na janey walon key liye unki apni maaon ki tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain. aur jo aadmi kisi Mujahid ki adam-mojudgi mein uski biwi key sath khayanat ka irtikab kerey. usey qiyamat key din us Mujahid key samney khada kar diya jaeyga. ke wo uski jitni nekiyan chahey ley ley, phir tumhara kya khayal hai? (kya wo uski koi neki chhod dega)."
3192,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujahideen ki aurten jang mein na janey walon key liye unki maaon ki tarah qabile-ehtiraam hain. jab koi shakhs kisi Mujahid key peechey rahey aur us (Mujahid) key ghar walon mein khayanat ka irtikab karey to qiyamat key din us Mujahid sey kaha jaeyga is ney terey ghar walon mein khayanat ki thi, lihaza to uski jitni nekiyan chahey ley ley. to tumhara kya khayal hai ( wo kuch chodega) ?"
3193,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujahideen ki aurton ka ehtiraam, gharon mein rehney walon key liye unki maaon key ehtiraam ki tarah hai. aur jihad sey peechey (gharon mein) rehney walon mein sey jo shakhs kisi Mujahid ki biwi key sath khayanat karey to usey qiyamat key din Mujahid key samney baandh kar khada kar diya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : aey falan! ye falan shakhs hai, to uski nekiyon mein sey jitni chahey ley ley. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sahaba ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : tumhara kya khayal hai ke wo uski koi neki chhod dega?"
3194,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney haathon, zabanon aur maalon key sath jihad karo."
3195,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sanp qatl karney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : jo shakhs unkey intiqam aur badley sey darta hai, wo hum mein sey nahin."
3196,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jabr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (merey walid mohtaram) Hazrat jabr (Raziallahu anhu) ki bimar pursi key liye tashrif laye. jab aap (ghar mein) dakhil huye to aap ney suna ke aurten ro rahi hain aur keh rahi hain ke hum to samajhti thin ke tum Allah key raastey mein shaheed hogey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum maqtool fi sabililah key ilawa kisi ko shaheed nahin samajhtey? phir to tumharey shaheed bahut kam hongey. Allah Taala key raastey mein maara jana shahadat hai, pet ki takleef sey faut hona bhi shahadat hai, aag mein jal kar mar jana bhi shahadat hai, doob kar mar jana bhi shahadat hai, kisi chiz key zariey dab kar mar jana bhi shahadat hai, nimoniya key zariey sey mar janey wala bhi shaheed hai aur jo aurat zachgi key doran mein faut ho jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai. eik aadmi ney un aurton sey kaha : tum roti ho jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : roney dey, albatta jab ye faut ho jaey to phir koi na roey."
3197,"Hazrat Jabr (haqiqat mein Jabir bin Ateek) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik qaribul-marg shakhs key yahan gaya. aurten roney lagin. mainey kaha tum roti ho jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma hain? aap ney farmaya : unhen roney dey. jab tak ye shakhs un mein zinda mojud hai, albatta jab ye faut ho jaey to koi roney wali na roey."
